name: Alphabet Print
description: A beautiful full colour lithographic print on heavyweight recycled stock with a matte finish (200gsm - FSC certified). The print measures 50cm x 40cm and is designed to fit a selection of off the shelf frames (frame shown not included). £5 from the first 200 prints sold will be donated to the Neonatal Intensive Care Unit at the Norfolk & Norwich University Hospital (Charity No. 1048170). More details about the print and information about the donation can be found here. If you are after a frame for the print this one fits a treat, and it's only £7. Each print will be carefully rolled in tissue paper and popped in a sturdy tube for delivery, so it gets to you looking lovely.

name: Happy Birthday Cards
description: Select your choice from the drop down menu below. The perfect card for any birthday boy or girl... choose from a flying rocket or a pretty bunch of flowers. Printed on 350gsm heavyweight, FSC Credited stock. The inside of the card has been left blank for you to write your own message and comes with a brown paper envelope. The card measures 105mm x 148mm (4.13" x 5.82").
